MY SIGNATURE BELOW ACKNOWLEDGES THAT:
1. I have read (or had read to me), understand and agree to the statements set forth in this consent form.
2. A physician or representative has explained to me all information referred to in this consent form. I have
had an opportunity to ask questions and my questions have been answered to my satisfaction, including any
question I have about the potential use of blood and/or blood products and any risks regarding their use.
3. All statements requiring completion were filled in before I signed.
4. No guarantees or assurances concerning the results of the procedure(s) have been made.
5. I am signing this consent voluntarily. I am not signing due to any coercion or other influence.
6. I hereby consent and authorize Dr. (my physician(s)) and/or those
associates, assistants and other health care providers designated by my physician(s) to perform the
