7. request my physician(s) or their designees to perform whatever medical acts or additional procedures they,
in the exercise of their sole professional judgment, deem reasonable and necessary, and I wave any obligation
on their part to stop or delay the continuation of my procedure to obtain additional consent if I am unable to
give additional consent at that time.
